Text: Ulyana Gordon: Thanks for sharing this! I was, to put it mildly, quite surprised to stumble across Eddie Lang torrents! Well, but that's the beauty of P2P, isn't it: You can share or find almost everything. By the way, Pickin' My Way is my favourite Eddie Lang-tune.
Ulyana...once again, a tremendous jazz share.  Thanks so much.  And for the other Eddie Lang too!
I'm trying to seed, but some of your links appear to be dead.  Thought you should know.  Thanks for the Tina Brooks!
